cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM

This paper is likely to belong to the Computer Vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with image synthesis and re-rendering. The Graphics (cs.GR) sub-category is also likely as it involves the traditional graphics pipeline. The use of learnable components suggests that it could also belong to the Machine Learning (cs.LG) and Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. Finally, the mention of video re-rendering and facial reenactment suggests that it could also belong to the Multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category.
